---
title: Creamy Chicken & Bacon Pie with Mash Potato Topping
description: We think the world's a better place when there's chicken pie for dinner! This one, with a creamy bacon and thyme sauce and heavenly mashed potato topping, is just the thing for a chilly winter's night. Get ready for a stampede when it comes to serving seconds!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-bacon-pie-426f0a9a.jpg
